<item>
            <title>[LU-7892] delete create_iam utility and references to it</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7892</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;lustre/utils/create_iam.c&lt;/tt&gt; utility was used at one point to format the OI file in userspace during MDT formatting.  However, this has not been needed for a long time since &lt;tt&gt;osd-ldiskfs&lt;/tt&gt; will create the OI file now, and it can be deleted.  There are several places in the code that reference &quot;create_iam&quot; in the comments that should also be deleted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
